{
  "text": "Another example of CPS architecture is proposed by [CITATION_1] for a CNC system. This CPS uses as well five layers such as (1) equipment, (2) sensing, (3) network, (4) cognitive, and (5) control. The three first layers represent the physical space, and the last two layers represent the cyberspace (cognitive and control).",
